<P><H1 align=center>APPLICATION SOURCE DETAILS – DC010</H1>
<P></P>
<P><FONT color=red><STRONG>NOTE: </STRONG>fields shown in red are mandatory and must be completed to 
proceed</FONT>         
  </P>
<P><H3>Direct or Indirect:</H3>select either option from the 
drop-down list. Direct would be an applicant who has applied direct to the 
lender, indirect would be where an applicant has applied via a third party such 
as a broker.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Special scheme: </H3>if the applicant is a staff 
member, select ‘Staff’ from the drop-down list. If not, select ‘None’
<P></P>
<P><H3>Marketing source: </H3>this is what prompted the 
applicant to make an enquiry / application eg. newspaper, TV, mailshot, internet 
etc. Select the relevant medium from the drop-down list
<P></P>
<P><H3>Nature of enquiry: </H3>whether the loan is residential 
or semi-commercial. This needs to be completed as there may be different <A href="HELP_MC010.asp#LendingCriteria">Lending criteria</A> for the different types
<P></P>
<P><H3>OK: </H3>when this screen has been completed, click 
‘OK’ to lead to the next screen.
